{{!-- Subject: Reservation confirmed for {{restaurantName}} --}}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Reservation Confirmation - {{restaurantName}}</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #e11d48;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }
        .confirmed-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #10b981, #059669);
            color: white;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .reservation-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0f9ff, #e0f2fe);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border: 2px solid #0ea5e9;
        }
        .restaurant-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 12px 0;
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #bae6fd;
        }
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #0c4a6e;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .detail-value {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1e293b;
            text-align: right;
        }
        .order-summary {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .order-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #111827;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .order-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin: 8px 0;
            padding: 8px 0;
        }
        .order-item-name {
            flex: 1;
            color: #374151;
        }
        .order-item-price {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #1f2937;
        }
        .total-row {
            border-top: 2px solid #e5e7eb;
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        .checkin-info {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border: 2px solid #f59e0b;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .checkin-title {
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .qr-placeholder {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: white;
            border: 2px dashed #d97706;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 15px auto;
            color: #92400e;
            font-size: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .btn-primary {
            background: #e11d48;
            color: white;
        }
        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            color: #374151;
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">La Carta</div>
            <div class="confirmed-badge">‚úì RESERVATION CONFIRMED</div>
        </div>

        <div class="greeting">
            All set, {{userName}}! üéâ
        </div>

        <p>Your reservation is confirmed and your pre-order is locked in. Everything is taken care of ‚Äì just show up and enjoy an incredible meal!</p>

        <div class="reservation-card">
            <div class="restaurant-name">{{restaurantName}}</div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">üìÖ Date & Time</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{reservationDate}} at {{reservationTime}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">üë• Party Size</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{partySize}} {{#if (gt partySize 1)}}guests{{else}}guest{{/if}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">ü™ë Table</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{#if tableNumber}}Table {{tableNumber}}{{else}}Assigned upon arrival{{/if}}</div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">üìç Address</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{restaurantAddress}}</div>
            </div>

            {{#if specialRequests}}
            <div class="detail-row">
                <div class="detail-label">üìù Special Requests</div>
                <div class="detail-value">{{specialRequests}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
        </div>

        {{#if hasPreOrder}}
        <div class="order-summary">
            <div class="order-title">üçΩÔ∏è Your Pre-Order</div>
            
            {{#each orderItems}}
            <div class="order-item">
                <div class="order-item-name">
                    {{quantity}}x {{name}}
                    {{#if modifiers}}<br><small style="color: #6b7280;">{{modifiers}}</small>{{/if}}
                </div>
                <div class="order-item-price">${{price}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/each}}
            
            <div class="order-item total-row">
                <div class="order-item-name">Subtotal</div>
                <div class="order-item-price">${{subtotal}}</div>
            </div>
            
            {{#if tax}}
            <div class="order-item">
                <div class="order-item-name">Tax</div>
                <div class="order-item-price">${{tax}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            {{#if tip}}
            <div class="order-item">
                <div class="order-item-name">Tip ({{tipPercent}}%)</div>
                <div class="order-item-price">${{tip}}</div>
            </div>
            {{/if}}
            
            <div class="order-item total-row" style="font-size: 18px; color: #e11d48;">
                <div class="order-item-name">Total Paid</div>
                <div class="order-item-price">${{totalAmount}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/if}}

        <div class="checkin-info">
            <div class="checkin-title">üì± Check-in Instructions</div>
            <p style="margin: 10px 0; color: #1f2937;">When you arrive, scan this QR code at your table to let the kitchen know you're seated. Your meal will be perfectly timed to arrive within 5 minutes!</p>
            
            <div class="qr-placeholder">
                QR Code<br>
                (Scan at table)
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin: 10px 0; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; text-align: center;">
                <strong>Reservation ID:</strong> {{reservationId}}
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="{{appUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}" class="btn btn-primary">View Reservation</a>
            <a href="{{appUrl}}/support/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Need Help?</a>
        </div>

        <p><strong>What to expect:</strong></p>
        <ul style="color: #374151; padding-left: 20px;">
            <li>Arrive at your reservation time ‚Äì your table will be ready</li>
            <li>Scan the QR code when you're seated to start the kitchen timer</li>
            <li>Your pre-ordered meal will arrive within 5 minutes, perfectly prepared</li>
            <li>Payment is complete ‚Äì just enjoy your dining experience!</li>
            <li>Rate your experience afterward to help us keep improving</li>
        </ul>

        {{#if restaurantPhone}}
        <p style="background: #f9fafb; padding: 15px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
            <strong>Restaurant Contact:</strong> <a href="tel:{{restaurantPhone}}" style="color: #e11d48;">{{restaurantPhone}}</a>
            <br><small style="color: #6b7280;">For same-day changes or special requests, call the restaurant directly.</small>
        </p>
        {{/if}}

        <p>We can't wait for you to experience the La Carta difference. Enjoy your meal!</p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>See you soon,<br>The La Carta Team</p>
            <p style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <strong>{{restaurantName}}</strong><br>
                <a href="{{appUrl}}/reservations/{{reservationId}}" style="color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none;">Manage Reservation</a> ‚Ä¢ 
                <a href="{{supportEmail}}" style="color: #6b7280; text-decoration: none;">Support</a>
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 12px;">
                ¬© {{year}} La Carta. All rights reserved.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>